# Content Authoring

## Blog (`src/content/blog/posts.ts`, `copywriter-posts.ts`, `editorial-posts.ts`)

- `BlogPost`: `slug`, `title`, `excerpt`, `category`, `date`, `author`, `coverImage`, `content[]`, `headings[]`.
- Slugs: kebab-case, unique, stable (URLs depend on them).
- `headings[].id` must match `##` anchor ids implied in markdown-style `content` blocks.
- `categories` is a non-empty array of valid `BlogCategory` keys (multiple badges per post).

## FAQ / pricing

- Keep structured data in `src/content/faqs.ts` and `src/content/pricing.ts`.
- UI reads content modules — avoid duplicating the same copy in components.

## Dates and locale

- ISO dates in content (`YYYY-MM-DD`); display formatting via `src/lib/blog.ts` / `toLocaleDateString("en-US")` until i18n exists.

## After adding blog posts

- No `generateStaticParams` change needed if slug is in `posts` array.
- Sitemap picks up slugs via `getAllSlugs()`.
